  "name": "RPlog_The_Infiltration",
  "title": "The Infiltration",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike slips into the Imperial-blockaded Chandrila system, where Admiral Danik Kreldin commands a fleet led by the Star Destroyer Conqueror. The retired captain of the Corellian gunship Lightbringer creeps toward the planet using space debris for cover, escorted by Republic fighters including Yellowtail's Ghost wing and the A-wings of Falcon Squadron, among them the Sullustan pilot Ikihsa Enb'Zik and squadron leader Evir Yissik. The gunship and fighters draw the Conqueror and its TIE squadrons into a swirling dogfight as a deliberate distraction. Meanwhile, on the far side of the world, the pilot Nynaeve in the Starkindler and the officer Stans in the shuttle Imperial Pain thread an incomplete minefield to slip dirtside undetected and land their infiltration team. Recognizing the ruse, Kreldin lets the landing ships go and dispatches ground ops to track them while the battered Lightbringer covers its fighters' retreat and jumps to hyperspace, its mission as a decoy accomplished.",
